{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/react-native-error-file-watchers-reached copy","webpackCompilationHash":"536f870586372e0b2ec1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"react-native-error-file-watchers-reached copy"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Native Error ENOSPC: System limit for number of file watchers reached on Linux","date":"August 10th, 2020","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/0ab32/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/a6209/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 375w,\n/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/849fc/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 750w,\n/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/0ab32/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 1500w,\n/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/656ff/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 2250w,\n/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/51810/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 3000w,\n/static/7113fd44d70a13e92075bcc6d274f9d0/b6d11/max-chen-lud4OaUCP4Q-unsplash.jpg 4032w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<p>Problem: Error when installing/running react native package on Linux</p>\n<p>Root Cause: The number of files monitored(hot reload) has reached the limit</p>\n<p>Solution:\nIncrease Inotify(package that Linux use to observe filesystem events) max limit</p>\n<ol>\n<li>open config file <code>$ sudo nano /etc/sysctl.conf</code></li>\n<li>add <code>fs.inotify.max_user_watches=524288</code> at the bottom file, save and exit</li>\n<li>load the new config <code>$ sudo sysctl -p</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Reference:\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/55763428/react-native-error-enospc-system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/55763428/react-native-error-enospc-system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached</a></p>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"react-native-error-file-watchers-reached copy"}}}